mixin Overview()
    section.overview
        .container.overview__container.reveal-zoom
            h2 Unlock New Levels of Strategy
            p We created a platform where basketball takes center stage, challenging your skills and tactics. Assemble your dream team and experience the thrill of every play!
            .overview__cards
                div.reveal-left
                    span 🏀 
                    h3 Create Your Roster
                    p Choose players who fit your unique playing style and take them to new heights.
                div.reveal-right
                    span 🎯 
                    h3 Tactical Mastery
                    p Sharpen your strategies and see how they shape the course of the game.
                div.reveal-left
                    span 🌍
                    h3 HoopsDynasty
                    p Dive into a world of basketball action, where every decision counts.
                div.reveal-right
                    span 🏆
                    h3 Build Your Legacy
                    p Shape your basketball dynasty with every game you play, from season to season.
